content.p: The School of English offers a range of programmes and degrees at all levels. The School offers two exciting undergraduate degrees or for those who want to enhance their study skills before joining an undergraduate course, we offer the Arts and Education Foundation. Students who already have a good undergraduate degree may be interested in pursuing a research degree - supervised by one of our members of academic staff. telephone: +603 8924 8000 fax: +603 8924 8001
